let mdImgRegex=/\!\[([^\]]+)?\]\(([^\)]+)\)/g;class ElementFormatter{get customEmotes(){return/(:don:|:katsu:|:desuwa:|:dirt:|:kib:)/g}get emojiTable(){return{don:"/static/svg/don.svg",katsu:"/static/svg/katsu.svg",desuwa:"/static/svg/desuwa.svg",dirt:"/static/image/dirt_small.gif",kib:"/static/svg/kib.svg"}}formatAll(){this.dateFormat(),this.markdownFormat(),this.twemojiFormat(),this.emoteFormat()}dateFormat(){for(let e of document.getElementsByClassName("date-format"))try{let t=luxon.DateTime.fromISO(e.innerHTML);e.innerHTML=t.toFormat("fff"),e.classList.contains("human-time")&&(e.innerHTML+=` (${t.toRelativeCalendar()})`)}catch(e){console.error(e)}}markdownFormat(){for(let e of document.getElementsByClassName("markdown-format")){let t=new showdown.Converter;try{e.innerHTML=DOMPurify.sanitize(t.makeHtml(e.innerHTML.replace(mdImgRegex,(e,t,o)=>`![${t||""}](https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=${o})`)),{USE_PROFILES:{html:!0}})}catch(e){console.error(e)}}}twemojiFormat(){for(let e of document.getElementsByClassName("twemoji-format"))try{twemoji.parse(e)}catch(e){console.error(e)}}emoteFormat(){for(let e of document.getElementsByClassName("emote-format"))try{e.innerHTML=e.innerHTML.replace(this.customEmotes,e=>{let t=document.createElement("img");return t.src=this.emojiTable[e.replace(/:/g,"")],t.className="emoji",t.draggable=!1,t.alt=e,t.outerHTML})}catch(e){console.error(e)}}}export{ElementFormatter};